criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Children with active carious lesions scores 1, 2 or 3 of the ICDAS in deciduous teeth

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with special needs;

          -  Patients using orthodontic appliances;

          -  systemic diseases;

          -  Teeth that present restorations, sealants, formation defects, deep caries lesions that
             may lead to pulp involvement, fistulae and / or abscesses;

          -  teeth with spontaneous painful symptomatology.
